name: D5 Skunk
description: Skunk, a half man/ half plant wearing a skin suit which morphs with your genes temporarily. This is his face when you discover him inside your house staring at you. This moments always scare the shit out of him (yeah you scream, he screams too).
collection_description: SuperRare makes it easy to create, sell, and collect rare digital art.
